# Token4Good v2 - Architecture Globale

## État du Projet : 85% Complété
**Production Target:** 28 octobre 2025

## Architecture Technique

### Backend (Rust + Axum) - 100% ✅
- Localisation : [token4good-backend/](mdc:token4good-backend/)
- Entry point : [token4good-backend/src/main.rs](mdc:token4good-backend/src/main.rs)
- Services principaux :
  - [rgb_native.rs](mdc:token4good-backend/src/services/rgb_native.rs) - RGB Protocol
  - [lightning.rs](mdc:token4good-backend/src/services/lightning.rs) - Lightning Network REST API
  - [database_services.rs](mdc:token4good-backend/src/services/database_services.rs) - PostgreSQL operations
- Routes API : [token4good-backend/src/routes/](mdc:token4good-backend/src/routes/)

### Frontend (Next.js 13) - 30% Migré ⚠️
- Localisation : [apps/dapp/](mdc:apps/dapp/)
- API Client : [apps/dapp/services/apiClient.ts](mdc:apps/dapp/services/apiClient.ts)
- PostgreSQL DAOs : [libs/service/data/src/lib/dao/](mdc:libs/service/data/src/lib/dao/)

### Base de Données
- PostgreSQL (Supabase) - Migration complète depuis MongoDB
- Schéma : [token4good-backend/migrations/](mdc:token4good-backend/migrations/)

## Stack Technique
- Backend : Rust + Axum + SQLx + PostgreSQL
- Frontend : Next.js 13 + React 18 + TypeScript
- Blockchain : RGB Protocol + Lightning Network (LND)
- Auth : JWT + OAuth (t4g, LinkedIn, Dazno)

